<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_128_r1l7"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> vns hat fürgelegt <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> <expan>weiſſemburg<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_128_r1l8"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> / 
<del rend="strikethrough">vvie</del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_128_line_1571064055441_59">vvie </ab></add> daʒ euch wol kündig ſeẏ v̈mb ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_128_r1l10">ſache 
<del rend="strikethrough">vnd <expan>v<ex>er</ex>luſte</expan> wie ſich die </del>
