<ab facs="#facs_128_r1l11"> <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr 
<del rend="strikethrough">durc </del> vns das an <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> brief / ſo Jr eygent </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_128_r1l12">licheſt künnet <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wiſſen laſſet / durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_128_r1l13">dinſte <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> / vvie eʒ darümb geſtalt ſeẏ / das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_128_r1l14">wir v̈mb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> in <expan>ſöliche<ex>n</ex></expan> oder merern <expan>ſach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
