</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_128" id="62v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der stat czu Kanme </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, uns hat fürgelegt
                            <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>
<expan>Weissemburg<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, <add>wie</add> daz euch wol kündig sey ümb
                        sein sache, <add>als sich an im</add>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>loffen</expan> und <expan>v<ex>er</ex>handelt</expan>
                        hab. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir uns das an
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> brief, so ir eygentlichest künnet,
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wissen lasset durch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> dinste
                        <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>, wie ez darümb gestalt sey. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ümb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> in <expan>söliche<ex>n</ex></expan> oder
                        merern <expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>.</ab>
</div>
